{
  "stem": "5388.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tadek brought them, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They got out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, it was only two, three houses left from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the whole Grodno ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was only two, three houses left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we left, there were already about five, six houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they went, it was already a few houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he took them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They have their own ride story-- quite a story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the thing looked like, suddenly, the liquidation of the Vilna ghetto is beginning to take place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm talking now summer, 1943.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Vilna ghetto, we lived on Strashun, 8.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a big kind of place with a yard and we managed to live there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- you know, in a room like that, would have been, maybe, three families living, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it was packed-- sardines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had-- we still had it pretty good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A smaller room where Leah, Aaron-- I don't know whether Aaron lived with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Aaron and my father and I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they went to-- my father worked, supposedly, in the electrical station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he used to go outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's where Aaron worked and his friend-- the other one, Lipshits.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't-- I used to prepare for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a big cook.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was getting horse meat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- they had even cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whoever heard?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jews getting ration cards in Grodno-- in, Vilna too, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You still got something there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- Did you hear at all about the Warsaw ghetto rebellion?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember too much details of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I knew that it was supposedly that people stood up in Warsaw and there was an uprising-- something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not too much detail, not too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
